						 <blockquote> <p>Wolves created through SCP-3900 do not exhibit wireless connectivity and are otherwise non-anomalous.</p> </blockquote> <p>This made me crack a smile, of <strong>course</strong> they'd test to see if they got wolf-fi.</p> <p>This is clever, and really fun to read. +1, and seriously, a breath of fresh air.</p> <p>Also, that testing log was one of the funniest, and best logs I've ever seen on the mainlist.</p> 
